text: Her onginneð kyþan ymbe þises middangeardes ylda.
Seo forma yld wæs Adame oð Noe, þæt is þonne þreo þusend wintra and sixandhundseofontig wintra.
Secunda Noe usque ad Abraham fuerunt anni CCC XCVIIðonne is seo oðer yld fram Noe oð Abraham, þæt is þonne þreo hund wintra.
Tertia Abraham usque ad Moysen, fuerunt anni DCCCC L XXðonne is seo ðridde yld fram Abrahame oð Moysen, þæt is þonne nigan hund wintra and hundseofantig wintra.

Quarta ad Moysen usque ad Dauid, fuerunt anni CCCC XCIII idem transmigrationem Babilonisðonne is seo feorðe yld fram Moysen oð Dauid, þæt is þonne feower hund wintra and ðreoandhundnigantig wintra þæs forðgewitenes þære miclan burche Babilonie.
Quinta ad Dauid usque ad Christum, fuerunt anni D L XXXVIIIðonne is seo fifte yld fram Dauid oð Crist, þæt is þonne fifhund wintra and niganandhundeahtatig wintra.

Sexta a natiuitate Domini usque in natale Domini uenit D CCCCC XLVIIIIðonne is seo sixte yld fram Cristes akennednesse agan, oð nu to middanwintre kimð, þæt is ðonne anþusend geara andVIIIIand hundnigantig geara.
Ab initio mundi usque in natiuitate Christi fuerunt anni quinque milia CXC VIIA natiuitate domini usque ad finem mundi fiunt autem anni D D XXVI
